        <h2>What is this?</h2>
        <p>Iconomus generates placeholder icons based on attributes you provide. So far, you can specify:</p>
        <p><span class="label">icon</span> <span class="label">color</span> <span class="label">opacity</span> <span class="label">rotation</span> <span class="label">size</span> <span class="label">format</span></p>
      </div>
